      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HAMMER ROSE (1) is struggling to break through but racing consistently, finishing in the minors four starts on end. Last time out flew the lids with a fast early sectional but gathered in and finished in the minors when third (22.73) at this track over 400m. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. Ready to find winning form. MEMORIES (7) has been in super consistent form recently with three minors on end before missing the frame latest finishing fourth (22.90) at this track. Has never been out of the placings from three starts out of this box. Can measure up this time. FAYE VALENTINE (3) finished well back at Horsham last time when a 5 length sixth (27.51) but scored five back at Shepparton (22.00). Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Likely to be about the money. PEAKY AVENGER (2) was in the money last start at big odds - poses a threat again.",
